org.microtitan.diffusive.diffuser.restful.resources.cache

Class ResultCacheEntry<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microtitan.diffusive.diffuser.restful.resources.cache.ResultCacheEntry<T>

  • public class ResultCacheEntry<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    The entry into the results cache. Each entry holds the results object and the serializer name used for serializing and deserializing the result object.
    Author:
    Robert Philipp
